{"type":"message","id":"2a12d02a","parentId":"e828b661","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:42:36.132Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<active-task-guard>\nSource: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\nStatus: active\nUse this only as the recovery rail for the current multi-step task.\nIf the user's latest message is a continuation, continue from Current, update ACTIVE_TASK.md after each minimum deliverable, and immediately promote the next item.\nIf the user's latest message is clearly unrelated, do not force this task.\n\nGoal:\n- 执行夜间研究会发布包，读取控制塔卡片，发送飞书卡片/摘要汇报\n\nAcceptance:\n- publish bundle 成功运行，输出 control tower card JSON / markdown\n- 飞书卡片/摘要成功发送\n- 中文汇报覆盖：主视图、审计状态、风险收缩、观察池、持仓预览、成交预览、数据源健康状态、临时会商状态\n\nCurrent:\n- 运行 `python3 scripts/run_investment_research_org_publish_bundle.py --meeting-type night`\n\nNext:\n- 读取 control tower card JSON / broadcast markdown\n- 发送飞书 interactive card 或 fallback 摘要\n- 汇报夜间研究会状态\n\nRecent Evidence:\n- No evidence recorded\n\nIntegrity Warnings:\n- None\n\nBlockers:\n- None\n</active-task-guard>\n\nSystem: [2026-03-21 20:31:43 GMT+8] Exec completed (briny-ri, code 0) :: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_review_ledger_20260321.md /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/investment_research_review_ledger_2…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 21st, 2026 — 8:42 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-21 12:42 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774096956131}}
