{"type":"message","id":"7daa3c64","parentId":"d7414410","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:44:38.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All tasks are done. Let me now provide a summary of what was accomplished.\n\nThe publish bundle ran successfully:\n- Generated all the expected output files\n- The automated Feishu card push failed (card JSON parse error) \n- I sent a text fallback message to 张玲 via DM successfully\n- The message covered all required areas: 主视图、审计状态、风险收缩、观察池、持仓预览、成交预览、数据源健康状态、临时会商状态\n\nLet me now reply with the summary.","thinkingSignature":"c67474ae3806b7160994d12cad2141a174d5128adefcc09fed050365b50933de"},{"type":"text","text":"夜间研究会发布包已执行完毕，汇报如下：\n\n**✅ 执行结果**\n- `publish bundle` 成功运行，生成全部报告文件（含控制塔卡片 JSON/MD、交易卡、首席看板、群聊摘要等）\n- 自动飞书卡片推送失败（卡片 JSON 解析错误，错误码 230099），已改用文本摘要通过飞书 DM 发送至张玲\n\n**📤 已发送飞书消息覆盖**\n| 维度 | 内容 |\n|---|---|\n| 主视图 | 夜间总览 |\n| 审计状态 | 通过，稳健通过 |\n| 风险收缩 | 是（偏防守） |\n| 观察池 | 暂无 |\n| 持仓预览 | 暂无 |\n| 成交预览 | 暂无 |\n| 数据源健康 | 非交易时段观察，可信度 80/100，THS 行情未知 |\n| 临时会商状态 | no_trigger，建议会商：否 |\n\n**⚠️ 关键提醒**\n- 模拟盘数据仍停留在 20260320（已过期）\n- 今日不能新开仓（大盘跌幅 -3.63% + 市场宽度 0.1167 双触发风控阈值）\n- 卖出复核：002173.SZ 创新医疗、002151.SZ 北斗星通\n- 08:50 晨报推送失败（最近成功 2026-03-16）\n\n**📁 产出文件路径**（已保存在 workspace）\n- 控制塔卡片：`research/reports/investment_research_control_tower_card_20260321.md`\n- 交易建议卡：`research/reports/investment_research_trade_card_night_20260321.md`\n- 总会纪要：`research/reports/investment_research_org_orchestrated_night_20260321.md`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10509,"output":483,"cacheRead":37969,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48961,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774097066162}}
